              	<p n="15-21"><supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>Inventory of two villages</foreign></supplied>.</p>
              	<p n="21-25"><gap reason="lost"/>: Si <gap reason="lost"/>, <gap reason="lost"/>, 2 babies, <gap reason="lost"/>. Among the <foreign>lvan</foreign>, there are 4 male slaves <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gho</foreign></supplied>, <gap reason="lost"/>.</p>
              	<p n="25-26"><gap reason="lost"/>, 3 male slaves <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gho</foreign></supplied>, an animal keeper <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gvāl</foreign></supplied>, <gap reason="lost"/>; total 11.</p>
